WEBVTT

16:51.880 --> 16:53.160 line:80%
Isn't that daylight robbery?

16:53.160 --> 16:53.830 line:80%
Exactly!

16:53.830 --> 16:55.490 line:80%
Our family can barely manage,

16:55.710 --> 16:57.920 line:80%
but those landless hired hands
and tenant farmers—

16:57.920 --> 16:59.400 line:80%
they have neither money nor grain.

16:59.400 --> 17:00.590 line:80%
And the New Year festival just passed.

17:00.590 --> 17:02.280 line:80%
What are they supposed to do?
